title: The Rolling Stones - L.A. Friday - Live 1975 - 320Kbps # DrBn
description:
RSAC Vol. 3

Mistitled by bootleggers back in the '70s as LA Friday, the recording was actually made on Sunday 13th July 1975, at the final performance of the Rolling Stones five night residency at the Los Angeles Forum. The show was part of the Rolling Stones Tour of the Americas . . .


THE ROLLING STONES

L.A. Friday
Live 1975

- 2 CD
- 2012
- 320Kbps

Recorded at the L.A. Forum, CA, Sunday, July 13th, 1975
Mixed by Bob Clearmountain
